verbose_text: The TNF induced activation of AKT and S6K1 could be blocked by Torin-1 and PP242 (XREF_FIG B), two specific inhibitors of both mTORC1 and mTORC2 functions, indicating that TNF specifically activates AKT and S6K1 via mTOR.
